document_data.caption: A map showing Canthrell between Norheim and Norland.
document_data.name: Canthrell
document_data.mainbody: '''Canthrell''' was an elongated island found between [[Norheim]] and [[Norland]] in the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: Moonshae Isles|11}}
document_data.Geography: Canthrell's was located between the [[Sea of Moonshae]] on its southeastern shores and the [[Trackless Sea]] to the northwest. It was the largest of a series of islands that almost joined Norheim and Norland in the northwest Moonshae Isles. Canthrell was {{SI|25|mi|k|long=yes}} long, but only {{SI|5|mi|k|long=yes}} wide at its widest point.
